track tads
superTrack on hide
shortLabel TADs
longLabel Topologically associating domains (TADs) and boundaries from Hi-C studies
group regulation
html tads

track tadsDixon
parent tads
priority 1
compositeTrack on
shortLabel Dixon 2012 TADs
longLabel TAD domains in hESC and IMR90 cells (Dixon et al. 2012, lifted from hg18)
type bigBed 4
group regulation
visibility pack
html tadsDixon

    track tadsDixonHESC
    parent tadsDixon on
    shortLabel hESC TADs
    longLabel TAD domains in H1 human embryonic stem cells (Dixon et al. 2012)
    type bigBed 4
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/bbi/tad/tadsDixonHESC.bb
    color 27,158,119
    mouseOver Cell type: $name (TAD domain)

    track tadsDixonIMR90
    parent tadsDixon on
    shortLabel IMR90 TADs
    longLabel TAD domains in IMR90 fetal lung fibroblasts (Dixon et al. 2012)
    type bigBed 4
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/bbi/tad/tadsDixonIMR90.bb
    color 217,95,2
    mouseOver Cell type: $name (TAD domain)

track tadsSchmitt
parent tads
priority 2
compositeTrack on
shortLabel Schmitt 2016 boundaries
longLabel TAD boundaries across 21 human tissues and cell lines (Schmitt et al. 2016)
type bigBed 4
group regulation
visibility hide
html tadsSchmitt
subGroup1 stype Sample_type cellLine=Cell_line tissue=Primary_tissue
subGroup2 organ Organ_system brain=Brain cardiovascular=Cardiovascular immune=Immune digestive=Digestive endocrine=Endocrine reproductive=Reproductive muscle=Muscle respiratory=Respiratory urinary=Urinary stem=Stem
dimensions dimX=organ dimY=stype
sortOrder stype=+ organ=+
showSubtrackColorOnUi on
allButtonPair on

    track tadsSchmittGM12878
    parent tadsSchmitt on
    shortLabel GM12878 bnd
    longLabel TAD boundaries in GM12878 lymphoblastoid cells (Schmitt et al. 2016)
    type bigBed 4
    bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/bbi/tad/tadsSchmittGM12878.bb
    subGroups stype=cellLine organ=immune
    color 51,160,44
    mouseOver Sample: GM12878 lymphoblastoid cells (TAD boundary, 40 kb bin)

