track tadsMcArthur
parent tads
priority 3
shortLabel TAD boundary stability
longLabel TAD boundary stability across 37 cell-type maps (McArthur & Capra 2021)
type bigBed 5 + 2
bigDataUrl /gbdb/$D/bbi/tad/tadsMcArthur.bb
group regulation
visibility hide
spectrum on
filter.contexts 4:37
filterByRange.contexts on
filterLimits.contexts 1:37
filterLabel.contexts Minimum number of cell-type maps sharing the boundary (1-37)
mouseOver Boundary recurrent in $contexts of 37 cell-type maps (percentile $percentile)
html tadsMcArthur

